63. Discover a function that takes an array of numbers as input and returns the sum of all the even numbers in the array.
ANSWER
<?php
function sumOfEvenNumbers($numbers) {
    $sum = 0;

    foreach ($numbers as $num) {
        if ($num % 2 == 0) {
            $sum += $num;
        }
    }

    return $sum;
}
// Example usage
$inputArray = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8];
$evenSum = sumOfEvenNumbers($inputArray);
echo "Sum of even numbers: " . $evenSum;
?>

OUTPUT
Sum of even numbers: 20
